---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Messy Careers - Career Coaching with Kate Mas"
    description="Career coaching with Kate Mas for professionals navigating a career change, leadership transition, or identity crisis. Based in Paris, working worldwide."
    transparentHeader={true}
>
    <!-- Hero — photo -->
    <section class="relative min-h-dvh flex items-end">
        <img
            src="/hero2.png"
            alt="Kate Mas"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" style="object-position: 70% center"
        />
        <!-- gradient scrim for text legibility -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 px-6 sm:px-10 md:px-12 lg:px-16 pt-24 pb-28 sm:pb-32 w-full md:w-1/2">
            <h1
                class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-6 leading-[1.05]"
            >
                <span class="block">Get clear on</span>
                <span class="block font-accent text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">
                    your next career move
                </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="font-sans text-base md:text-lg text-white/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Career strategy & coaching for leaders in the messy middle — stuck, uncertain but ready for something different.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-8">
                <a href="/intro-call" class="btn-white">Let's talk</a>
                <a href="/reviews" class="btn-outline-white">Client stories</a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-10">
                <p class="font-sans text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/50 mb-3">Trusted by clients from</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:flex sm:flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-4 sm:gap-y-3">
                    <img src="/Microsoft-logo.webp" alt="Microsoft" class="h-4 sm:h-5 w-auto max-w-[90px] object-contain object-left opacity-50 brightness-0 invert" />
                    <img src="/Preply_logo_(2023).svg.png" alt="Preply" class="h-4 sm:h-5 w-auto max-w-[90px] object-contain object-left opacity-50 brightness-0 invert" />
                    <img src="/qonto-2022.svg" alt="Qonto" class="h-4 sm:h-5 w-auto max-w-[90px] object-contain object-left opacity-50 brightness-0 invert" />
                    <img src="/International_Watch_Company_logo.svg.png" alt="IWC" class="h-4 sm:h-5 w-auto max-w-[90px] object-contain object-left opacity-50 brightness-0 invert" />
                    <img src="/Ogury_Logos_Black-1.png" alt="Ogury" class="h-4 sm:h-5 w-auto max-w-[90px] object-contain object-left opacity-50 brightness-0 invert" />
                    <img src="/DeepL_logo.svg" alt="DeepL" class="h-4 sm:h-5 w-auto max-w-[90px] object-contain object-left opacity-50 brightness-0 invert" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 1 — BLUE: Bio -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-primary text-primary-foreground">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary mb-6">
                    Hi, I'm Kate
                </p>
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight">
                    Your career doesn't have to be linear
                </h2>
                <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-primary-foreground/70 mb-6">
                    I spent 8+ years working in tech — across edtech and fintech
                    — eventually leading teams as a manager. I was good at my
                    job. But what I kept coming back to, in every role, was the
                    people side: the difficult conversations, the career
                    crossroads, the moments when someone needed to be seen.
                </p>
                <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-primary-foreground/70 mb-10">
                    So I made my own pivot. I retrained as a coach, earned my
                    ICF ACC accreditation, and have since worked with 150+
                    clients navigating their own messy career stories. Part of
                    what I bring is lived experience — including the wrong turns,
                    so you don't have to make them too.
                </p>
                <a href="/about" class="link-arrow-white">
                    More about me
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2 — BEIGE: People come to me when… -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-background">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary/50 text-center mb-4">
                Sound familiar?
            </p>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-foreground text-center mb-8 sm:mb-10">
                People come to me when…
            </h2>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"I don't know what I want anymore"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"I need to change direction — but how?"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"I've been stuck for a while and I can't figure out why"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"I've lost sight of what actually matters to me"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"I feel like I'm playing a role that isn't really mine"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"My job is taking over my life"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"Everything changed — now what?"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"I just need help figuring out what I actually want"</span>
                <span class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 sm:px-5 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-2xl">"I'm stepping into leadership and need to figure out who I am in this role"</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4 — BLUE: Coaching Services -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-primary text-primary-foreground">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-16">
                <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary mb-4">
                    How I can help
                </p>
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">
                    Ways to work together
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 sm:gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <div class="bg-primary-foreground/10 border border-primary-foreground/20 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-primary-foreground/15 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <span class="font-serif text-xl text-primary">1</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary-foreground mb-4">
                        1-to-1 Coaching
                    </h3>
                    <p class="font-sans text-primary-foreground/70">
                        Personalized sessions to get unstuck, gain clarity, and
                        move forward — whether you're navigating a career change
                        or stepping into a new kind of leadership.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary-foreground/10 border border-primary-foreground/20 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-primary-foreground/15 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <span class="font-serif text-xl text-primary">2</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary-foreground mb-4">
                        Corporate Training
                    </h3>
                    <p class="font-sans text-primary-foreground/70">
                        Workshops and coaching programmes for teams navigating
                        change, growth, or career development at scale.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-8 sm:mt-10">
                <a href="/services" class="link-arrow-white">
                    Find the right fit
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5 — BEIGE: Client stories -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-background">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-16">
                <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-4">
                    Client stories
                </p>
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-foreground">
                    What people say
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Career growth</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-base sm:text-lg text-foreground leading-snug flex-grow mb-5">
                        "She helps you uncover solutions you didn't even know you had in you."
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Daria L.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Life pivot</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-base sm:text-lg text-foreground leading-snug flex-grow mb-5">
                        "Kate helped me dig out a much bigger problem — and move forward with a truly pivotal decision for me and my family."
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Anonymous</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Career clarity</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-base sm:text-lg text-foreground leading-snug flex-grow mb-5">
                        "Kate's approach helped me see myself and my potential in a new light."
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Yana A.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-8 sm:mt-10">
                <a href="/reviews" class="link-arrow">
                    Read all stories
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6 — BLUE: Final CTA -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-primary text-primary-foreground">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 text-center">
            <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary mb-4">
                First step
            </p>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 sm:mb-8">
                Not sure where to start?
            </h2>
            <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-primary-foreground/80 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 sm:mb-10">
                Book a free intro call. We'll talk about what's going on,
                what you're hoping to change, and whether we're a good fit.
                No pressure, no pitch.
            </p>
            <a href="/intro-call" class="btn-white btn-lg">Let's talk</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
